 {"id":"7lmmtyt","platform":"ig","type":"Static Post","title":"Summer solstice — longest day of the year","description":"\"June 21 — the longest day of the year. In yoga, the solstice is a time of peak energy and an invitation to pause. What are you welcoming into this season? Join us on the mat. Summer Reset Pass still open — link in bio.\"\nWellness-forward, seasonal, soft. This is one of the strongest organic hooks of the summer. Faye may want to write this one — it's very brand-voice.","uses":"","assignee":"Alisa","status":"assigned","week":3,"pipeline":{"go_live": "2026-06-19", "in_buffer": "2026-06-15", "caption_due": "", "owner_proof": "2026-06-12"},"tags":[],"blocker":"","approval":"","subtasks":[],"created_at":"2026-05-27T16:13:23.318946+00:00","updated_at":"2026-05-27T16:13:23.318946+00:00"}, 
